data.description: Great floor plan on the edge of a quiet cul-de-sac. 2 story Great Room opens to a breakfast area & kitchen w/granite & tile backsplash. The primary bedroom is on the main floor w/ trey ceiling, garden tub, sep shower, dual vanities, & huge closet. Bedrooms 2 & 3 are a good size and bedroom 4/bonus is massive w/2 walk in closets. The upstairs loft area is great for office, TV room, hobby area, etc.. The 2 car garage leads into mud/laundry room. Tiled back patio w/ lush, flat, fenced backyard. The roof and HVAC were replaced in 2023.
